Text: When i arrived to Lisboa i couldnt believe how wonderful and friebdly was the
  people, i felt like home. The streets full od colours and good smells it was living
  a dream, magics days in a paradise place. I hardly recommend everybody at least
  once in their luves to visit this amazing country.I will tell you all the tips and
  profits to make sure your stay will be perfect as you plan!
